Metadata-Version: 1.0
Name: pypdflib
Version: 0.1.a3
Summary: PangoCairo based Python PDF Library
Home-page: https://savannah.nongnu.org/projects/pypdflib
Author: Santhosh Thottingal
Author-email: santhosh.thottingal@gmail.com
License: LGPL 3.0
Description: pypdflib: Python based PDF Rendering Library
        ============================================
        
        Features:
        ---------------------------
        * Uses Pango Cairo for rendering
        * Supports Complex scripts such as Indic scripts
        
        How to Install:
        ---------------------------
        
        1. Get the sourcecode
        
                git clone http://git.gitorious.org/pypdflib/pypdflib.git
        			or
                git clone http://github.com/santhoshtr/pypdflib.git
        
        2. Create the eggs
        
                python setup.py build
        
        3. Install the library
        
                sudo python setup.py install 
        
